description
Remembering that this is not GTA IV for ps2 because it does not exist for ps2, this game is just the GTA San Andreas modified to be similar to GTA IV.
Added to the game:
- City of Sao Paulo, Rio de Janeiro and Belo Horizonte
- Shops-known: Casas Bahia, Hundred Stores, FNAC, Post, Ponto Frio, Bradesco, Magazine Luiza, Rede Globo, Carrefour, Big, American Stores and more;
- New characters: Jason, Panico, biker Phantom, Catwoman, Homer Simpsons, Woman Fern and others
- Menu in Portuguese;
- Menu codes;
- Radio National, Transamerica, Peter Pan, Educator, New Wave and others;
- Cops: BOPE, PM, Civil Police, Caveirão and more;
- Bags of Brazil's most popular teams (Corinthians, São Paulo, Palmeitas, Santos, Portuguese, Bahia, Vitoria, Vasco, Botafogo, Fluminense, Flamento, Cruise, Atlético / MG, Parana, Coritiba, athletic / PR, Figueirense, Criciuma, Guild, International, Youth, CRB, American / RN, Goiás, São Raimundo / AM, Guarani, Ponte Preta, Mogi Mirim, Fortaleza, Naútico, Santa Cruz, Sport Recife and others.
